      hr
      .section#shop.foo2.generallydisabled
        style .shopItem .desc{display:none} 
        .title.is-2: b Event Cash Shop
        .subtitle.is-4 Don't want to wait? Get your items right away and support Pollux <b>and</b> the Artists!               
        .container  
          .notification.is-warning
            p 
              | All items in this list can be obtained for free if you participate in the event! Consider getting them naturally to not spoil the fun of obtaining it.
              br
              | <b>The only exception being the ones from the Team you don't belong to.</b>
          p If you still want to do it just get them right away, there you go:
        
          -var shopstock = buyables.filter(item=>item.filter.split(' ').includes('halloween18'))
          include ../store/compositestore
        .help
          | Purchases made here are processed automatically and aren't reversible.
          br
          //| 30% of all money goes to the Artists, 40% to Pollux development, 30% is dedicated to cover processing, bank transfer, and currency conversion fees.
          
      
      
      hr
      .section#participating.foo2
        .columns.is-marginless
          .column.is-6
            .section 
              .title.b500T Participating as a Server
              br
              .subtitle: b Joining
              p Owners of verified/eligible servers can use <code>p!event boxes</code> to get free Event Lootboxes to be distributed amongst your members.
              p Each one will receive 5 Event Lootboxes, one of every Rarity Tier + 1 Common Event Lootbox for every 100 members in their servers, capping in 15 total.
              hr
              .subtitle: b Put your hands in the Hypekit!
              p Set up a cool event info channel with the hypekit provided 
                a(href="#hypekit") here
              hr
              .subtitle: b Eligibility
              p Not all Servers will be receive the special event boxes, because there are always those who will not play fairly. So, for your Server be automatically Eligible, you will need to match all these criteria:
              ul(style="list-style: initial;padding:12px;")
                li Your Server has a Human : Bot ratio below 10%
                li Your Server must have been created before August 15th
                li Pollux must be in your server since August 15th or before
              br
              small For the last two items, you can still have your server included by asking for a whitelist, join the Support Server to be verified and whitelisted. 
      
          .column.is-6
            .section
              .title.b500T Participating as a User
              br
              .subtitle: b First things first
              p To start participating, you need to pick a team. Type <code>p!eventjoin</code> and go through the steps to choose your team, be wary that your decision is not reversible. Opting in for a team's rewards excludes you from the others. CHOOSE WISELY 

              hr
              .subtitle: b Show your participation
              p Add an event frame to your profile pic with <code>p!evpropic</code>. You will receive a generous bonus from it!
              
              hr
              .subtitle: b Collect collect collect!
              p Show your team's might by collecting as much Flowers/Snowflakes as you can, do this with <code>p!collect</code>. The more you dive into the event, the more you will receive. Completing Milestones grant you bonus items, changing your profile picture to your team's motif will boost considerably your income!
              
              hr
              .subtitle: b A little bit of cheating, get your items from second-hand market!
              p Australis is lurking around, you can get some Snowflakes and Flowers from her, they ain't cheap, but buying from her will boost the Lootbox Drop Rate in your server. Call her <code>p!trader [Amount]</code>, and don't look at her chest for too long, or she will complain and you'll be dragged out of her shop.              
              
              hr
              .subtitle: b Deliver!
              p Turn in your items to the Priestesses using <code>p!deliver [Amount]</code>
              p The more you turn in, the faster you team will reach Milestones and receive global Event Goodies, deliver more at once to receive better prizes!
              
              hr
              .subtitle: b Stay tuned in the Leaderboards!
              p Top deliverers will receive some special treats at the end of the event!
              p Use <code>p!evboard</code> regularly to check the competition!
              p Use <code>p!evtop [SFK/FLW]</code> to check user Leaderboards!

    
      hr
      .section#logs.foo2
        .title.is-2: b Solstice Saga Event Logs
        .subtitle.is-4 There's so much going on among the teams, so check here a resume of everything.
        br

        //.message.is-info
          .message-header Thursday September 20th
          .message-body 
            p • The third Snowflakes and Flowers ministers were elected by the team members.
            p: br
            p • <a href="/p/103727554644418560">Kat#2805</a> keeps in the house but this time sitting in the Minister's throne for Snowflakes (SFK)
            //p  -  with <a href="/p/  ">   </a> as his secretary.
            p: br
            p • <a href="/p/138719997315907584">Krispy Chips#3574</a> joins in for Flowers (FLW)
            //p  -  with <a href="/p/  ">   </a> as his secretary, refreshing completely the population in the ministry house. 
            p: br
            //p • Both were subjected to a challenge where they have to make some tough choices. Ending up in a +10 bonus for FLW, and access to classified information to SFK. Plus a exclusive event BG to everyone;
            
        .message.is-purple
          .message-header Wednesday September 19th
          .message-body 
            p • New Ministers elections start!
            p • <a href="/p/103727554644418560">Kat#2805</a> leads the elections with over 60 votes out of 75 total.
            p • Flowers have a tight competition for their new leader. <a href="/p/279666399486541824">Gustavo Sith神#6395</a> and <a href="/p/138719997315907584">Krispy Chips#3574</a> head to head.
            p: br
            p: b • Flowers elections presumedly rigged for <a href="/p/279666399486541824">Gustavo Sith神#6395</a>, Flowers concerned. Some withdraw their votes. 
            
        .message
          .message-header Sunday September 16th
          .message-body 
            p • Flowers opt in for some boosts and adopts Ministry Decree Bonus
            p • Snowflakes pay 200K of their flakes to reduce the collect cooldown

        .message.is-ruby
          .message-header Friday September 14th
          .message-body 
            p: b • On the verge of being overthrown, Flowers Minister resigns due to pressure of the masses and negative press coverage. electricas#8005 assumes the post of interim Flowers Minister.
            p
            p • After some commotion. <a href="/p/320351832268472320">Howerr#0956</a> is promoted to Flowers Minister and <a href="/p/163200584189476865">electricas#8005</a> keeps in the ministry house as his Secretary
            p
            p • Previously swapped members are unswapped.
            p
            p: b • Beginning of the Solstice mutual-interest treaty:
            p  -  Flowers and Snowflakes collectively extinguish the burn penalty
            p  -  Snowflakes income increased by Ministry decree for 50K Snowflakes
            p  -  Flowers declares sportsmanship status and neither buy more income, nor denies SFK's income.

            
                
        .message.is-danger
          .message-header Thursday September 13th
          .message-body 
            p • Ministers challenge was carried and resulted in mutual burn, penalising both teams with -100 at collect.
            p: br
            p: b • Tension ensues among Solsticelings, the first solstice crisis begins.
            p • Flowers Minister begins his autocratic regime.
            p • Snowflakes Minister tries to handle the situation.
            
            
        .message.is-info
          .message-header Wednesday September 12th
          .message-body 
            p: b • New ministers elected.
            p • <a href="/p/133004786562760704">key#8305</a> for Snowflakes
            p  -  with <a href="/p/103727554644418560">Kat#2805</a> as his secretary.
            p • <code>[REDACTED]</code> for Flowers
            p  -  with <a href="/p/320351832268472320">Howerr#0956</a> as his secretary.
            p: br 
            p • Ministers prompted to swap around 2 of its members.
            p: br 
            p: b • Swapped to SFK
            p  -  <a href="/p/114115657871654920">Meowkey#6849</a>
            p  -  <a href="/p/266133831671742464">Ehdward#0001</a>
            p: br 
            p: b • Swapped to FLW
            p  -  <a href="/p/423349777011310593">☭ᴠʟᴀᴅɪᴍɪʀ ɪʟʏɪᴄʜ ᴜʟʏᴀɴᴏᴠ☭#4196</a>
            p  -  <a href="/p/271808225148534784">Mati#1953</a>
            
            
            
        .message
          .message-header Tuesday September 11th
          .message-body 
            p • The Haze has dissipated, bonus removed.
        
        .message
          .message-header Monday September 10th
          .message-body 
            p • Event guides added by flowers on reddit.
            p • Melting Rate kicked-in. Removing 1% of every delivered flakes/flowers every 5 minutes
                    
        .message.is-purple
          .message-header Saturday September 8th
          .message-body 
            p • THE HAZE has been introduced, event status obfuscated by a thick myst. Also +50 Haze bonus to everyone.
                    
        .message.is-success
          .message-header Thursday September 6th
          .message-body 
            p • First Milestone Reached!
            p: br
            p • Mini event bonus ended, every one got 1 UR Summer/Winter Lootbox +  1 UR Neutral event box.
           
            
        .message.is-info
          .message-header Tuesday September 4th
          .message-body 
            p • The first Snowflakes and Flowers ministers were elected by the team members.
            p: br
            p • <a href="/p/423349777011310593">☭ᴠʟᴀᴅɪᴍɪʀ ɪʟʏɪᴄʜ ᴜʟʏᴀɴᴏᴠ☭#4196</a> for Snowflakes (SFK)
            p  -  with <a href="/p/103727554644418560">Kat#2805</a> as his secretary.
            p: br
            p • <a href="/p/114115657871654920">Meowkey#6849</a> for Flowers (FLW)
            p  -  with <a href="/p/320351832268472320">Howerr#0956</a> as his secretary.
            p: br
            p • Both were subjected to a challenge where they have to make some tough choices. Ending up in a +10 bonus for FLW, and access to classified information to SFK. Plus a exclusive event BG to everyone;
        
      hr
